OL,7,FSimone White lived life with such
OL,8,Firrepressible energy, that her friends
OL,9,Fand family say it was hard to keep up.
OL,11,F"She just loved life and used to make
OL,12,Fthe most of every minute," her mother
OL,13,FSue White told ITV News.
OL,15,FShe describes her daughter as "very
OL,16,Fextroverted, hugely popular - loved to
OL,17,Fplay hard and work hard. She was
OL,18,Fvibrant, sporty, musical".
OL,20,FThe 28-year-old lawyer from Orpington
OL,21,Fin Kent also loved to travel.
