OL,7,FSimone and her best friend Bethany had
OL,8,Fbeen all over the world, and their
OL,9,Ftrip to Cambodia and Laos in November
OL,10,Flast year was meant to be their next
OL,11,Fgreat adventure.
OL,13,FA couple of days into the holiday,
OL,14,FSimone's mother realised she hadn't
OL,15,Fheard from her so she sent her a
OL,16,Fmessage to check if everything was ok.
OL,18,F"She literally came straight back and
OL,19,Fsaid, yeah, it's the best trip I've
OL,20,Fdone, I'm having the time of my life,"
OL,21,FSue told me.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/22
