OL,7,F"And that's the last time I heard from
OL,8,Fher."
OL,10,FThat evening, Simone, Bethany and
OL,11,Fanother friend went to the bar at the
OL,12,FNana Backpacker's Hostel where they
OL,13,Fwere staying in Vang Vieng, Laos.
OL,15,F"They told us it would be free whiskey
OL,16,For free vodka shots," Bethany said.
OL,18,F"We don't really drink shots, so we
OL,19,Fwere like, okay, we'll just get
OL,20,Fmixers."
