OL,7,FShe said she watched the bartender
OL,8,Fpour the shots from a "typical vodka
OL,9,Fbottle" and then ordered Sprite to mix
OL,10,Fthem with.
OL,12,FBethany remembers them ordering five
OL,13,For six shots each over the course of
OL,14,Ftwo and half hours and said she didn't
OL,15,Fnotice anything untoward, apart from
OL,16,Fthe fact that the drinks didn't taste
OL,17,Fas strong as she would have expected.
OL,19,F"We just felt a bit off": Simone's
OL,20,Ffriend, Bethany, describes when they
OL,21,Fboth started to feel unwell
