OL,7,F"I just felt that I should have felt
OL,8,F(the effect of the alcohol) more than
OL,9,FI did," she told me.
OL,11,FIt wasn't until the next day that they
OL,12,Fstarted to feel unwell. Bethany
OL,13,Frecalls waking up at 8.30 am the next
OL,14,Fmorning with what she initially
OL,15,Fthought was a "mild" hangover.
OL,17,F"We just felt a bit off. I can't
OL,18,Freally describe what exactly it was,
OL,19,Fbut it wasn't like your typical
OL,20,Fhangover."
