OL,7,FThey had booked a swimming excursion
OL,8,Fbut, when they arrived, Bethany said,
OL,9,Fneither she nor Simone wanted to swim.
OL,11,FShe describes feeling tired,
OL,12,Flethargic, and "heavy".
OL,14,F"Just not really being able to move
OL,15,Fthe muscles that you want to move when
OL,16,Fyou want to move them."
