OL,7,FWhen it came to kayaking, Bethany
OL,8,Fdescribed how she and Simone could
OL,9,Fonly "lay on the back of the kayaks,"
OL,10,Fwhile someone else had to paddle for
OL,11,Fthem.
OL,13,FWhen Simone started being sick, and
OL,14,FBethany fainted, their friend
OL,15,Fsuggested they should all go to a
OL,16,Fhospital.
OL,18,FMore than 24 hours after consuming the
OL,19,Fpoisonous drinks, Bethany said
OL,20,FSimone's condition was deteriorating
OL,21,Frapidly
