OL,7,FBethany said that when they arrived,
OL,8,Fstaff at the public hospital in
OL,9,FVientiane initially wrongly suspected
OL,10,Feither food poisoning or drugs. All
OL,11,Fthree were given treatment, but by
OL,12,Fthis time Simone's condition was
OL,13,Fdeteriorating rapidly.
OL,15,F"Her breathing started to change, she
OL,16,Fwasn't able to look at me in the eye,
OL,17,Fshe was just sort of looking into the
OL,18,Fdistance," Bethany said.
OL,20,F"I just didn't know what to do."
