OL,7,FThe friends made the decision to be
OL,8,Ftransferred to a private hospital but,
OL,9,Fby the time they arrived there, more
OL,10,Fthan 24 hours after consuming the
OL,11,Fpoisonous drinks, "it was just too
OL,12,Flate", said Bethany.
OL,14,F"They just said to me, can you sign
OL,15,Fthese forms? We'll do all we can to
OL,16,Fsave her life."
OL,18,FThe next morning, Sue woke up to a
OL,19,Fmessage from Bethany. It said "I don't
OL,20,Fwant to worry you, but we're all in
OL,21,Fhospital with acidosis."
