OL,7,FIt explained that doctors said Simone
OL,8,Fwas showing signs of improvement, but
OL,9,Fshe was still sedated.
OL,11,FSue booked herself on a flight to Laos
OL,12,Fso she could be there when her
OL,13,Fdaughter woke up.
OL,15,F"I thought, 'oh, she's in a serious
OL,16,Fcondition, but she'll pull through
OL,17,Fand, you know, she'll be in hospital
OL,18,Ffor a few days'."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/22
