OL,7,FShe arrived just as they were wheeling
OL,8,FSimone into surgery, but it didn't go
OL,9,Fwell.
OL,11,F"We were told on the Sunday evening,
OL,12,Fafter the CT scan, that she only had
OL,13,F5% brain power. And then by the Monday
OL,14,Fit had gone down to zero.
OL,16,F"We knew that she wasn't going to
OL,17,Fsurvive. So, it was just a case of
OL,18,Fwaiting. I just felt sick," Sue said.
