OL,7,FSue and Bethany sat for days by
OL,8,FSimone's bedside, talking to her, and
OL,9,Fplaying voice notes that had been sent
OL,10,Fby her friends.
OL,12,F"We just told her how much she was
OL,13,Floved and how much she'd be missed
OL,14,Fhopefully she did hear something.
OL,16,F"I'm so grateful I was there by her
OL,17,Fbedside", Sue said, "But it was
OL,18,Fabsolutely soul destroying. Obviously
OL,19,Fthat picture is going to be in my mind
OL,20,Fforevermore."
