OL,7,FSimone's mother, Sue, said she was
OL,8,Ftold by doctors that she would have to
OL,9,Fturn her daughter's life support off
OL,10,Fherself
OL,12,FSue said that doctors eventually
OL,13,Fexplained to her that they couldn't
OL,14,Fswitch off Simone's life support for
OL,15,Freligious reasons. She was told she
OL,16,Fwould have to do it herself.
OL,18,F"It was awful. I had my husband and my
OL,19,Fson on the end of the phone, but I was
OL,20,Fin the room on my own.
