OL,7,F"Nothing will ever compare to that,
OL,8,Fwhat we all had to go through in that
OL,9,Fhospital. It was just devastating,"
OL,10,Fshe said.
OL,12,FThe reason Sue and Bethany are
OL,13,Fspeaking about what happened to Simone
OL,14,Fis because they want to stop it from
OL,15,Fhappening to anybody else.
OL,17,FBethany has started a petition for UK
OL,18,Fschools to educate children about
OL,19,Fmethanol poisoning, in the same way
OL,20,Fpeople are warned about the dangers of
OL,21,Fdrink spiking.
