OL,7,F"It's not something I was taught about
OL,8,Fat school. None of us knew about it,"
OL,9,Fshe said.
OL,11,FSue is calling for testing strips to
OL,12,Fbe made widely available at an
OL,13,Faffordable cost for travellers, so
OL,14,Fthey can test their drinks for
OL,15,Fmethanol before they consume them.
OL,17,FSimone was one of six tourists who
OL,18,Fdied after staying at the Nana
OL,19,FBackpacker Hostel, which has since
OL,20,Fbeen closed down and it is not known
OL,21,Fwhen it will open again.
