OL,12,Fthe status of this is unknown. ITV
OL,13,FNews has approached the Laos
OL,14,Fauthorities but has not heard back.
OL,16,FSue and Bethany told me that the
OL,17,Fpolice investigation in Laos is yet to
OL,18,Fprovide them with any answers. They
OL,19,Ffear they will never know who was
